{"tid":503469,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亞太7地調查　港打工仔最悲觀","createTime":"2017-12-19T01:11:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-19T05:43:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d5bd593f458e369192b1caed38ba65b447b5d996","tid":503469,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T01:11:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171219/20249068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F20249068&d=OOlVbkzSc%2FpoKpTIQIzIf%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=573c6813\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171219%2F20249068&h=fd3ea8d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171219/20249068</a><br />\n<br />\n亞太7地調查　港打工仔最悲觀<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171219/large/16735804.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171219%2Flarge%2F16735804.jpg&h=4c3ea16a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港打工仔是亞太區中最不快樂。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】有調查顯示，本港僅三成打工仔對目前工作感到快樂，快樂指數10分中只得4.45分，不愉快的最大原因是公司管理不善，以行業劃分，從事IT的僱員最不快樂。<br />\n<br />\nADVERTISING<br />\n<br />\n逾四成不快樂 IT界最差<br />\n<br />\n招聘網站jobsDB於港、星、馬、泰、越、菲、印亞太區7地進行工作快樂程度調查，本港今年8月訪問1,470名在職人士，10分為快樂指數滿分，本港打工仔只得4.45分，比榜末新加坡4.31分略高，本港僱員有42%表示不快樂、28%表示中立、30%表示快樂。<br />\n<br />\n不快樂的三大因素依次為公司管理模式不善、缺乏晉升機會、缺乏培訓及進修機會。各行業中，從事IT（硬件）、企業財務、電子或通訊工程的僱員最不快樂，初級職員、中層至經理級僱員較不快樂。開工快樂的原因依次為工作地點、公司聲譽及與同事關係理想，快樂的行業有電機工程、人力資源、酒店或旅遊。<br />\n<br />\n本港僱員對工作前景更是7地中最悲觀，展望半年後快樂指數降至4.18分，25%人對目前工作沒有期望，認為辭職轉工才能更快樂；21%人認為加薪會較快樂；11%人希望公司可多予以表揚和獎賞，分別有7%人希望升職、放假使他們工作開心一點。<br />\n<br />\njobsDB香港區行政總裁仇崑石指，調查反映不少人因工作不愉快轉工，經理更是最不快樂的職級。他提醒僱主提供合理待遇已是基本要求，員工是企業的寶貴資產，若長期忽視他們的需求難免令人萌生去意，而留任員工若帶負面情緒工作亦礙發揮表現，長久也會影響公司業務，建議僱主多檢討管理方針，並向各級職員提供持續培訓及進修機會，改善工作氛圍。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁楚雙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20171219/large/a0406a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171219%2Flarge%2Fa0406a.gif&h=f93e38e6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be76b3aff18666b448e9c2315ff818a15629d845","tid":503469,"uid":106641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T01:41:41.000Z","msg":"老貓召喚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5bb674114167f70c59b51ad7e83618fa53a925f","tid":503469,"uid":51041,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T01:48:37.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔好用氛圍呢個字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好撚7<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd89656be5e060261496c0c9ab9cc39eb64d589","tid":503469,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T01:51:33.000Z","msg":"IT(<span style=\"color: red;\">硬件</span>) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91fc854aa08c07c4b7f7535c8b9600487420b80","tid":503469,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:43:08.000Z","msg":"快唔快樂因素竟然唔係用人工同工時做指標<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e77643dd4e94974d7b11df088909a51f234046b2","tid":503469,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:45:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"def0f08b9e2b21974c1b9a065346eb6122d55527","tid":503469,"uid":134864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04:52:40.000Z","msg":"IT狗又中槍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3680e8a5303f133cf5d1ebe2129c26e99893c4f9","tid":503469,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T04